      propertyPath: 'dialogueLines.Array.data[0]'
      value: The guards, soldiers, and loyalists of the Usurper have been recalled
        to the Capital...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3292689138879906966, guid: ecbba99a1b1a2e848813fba8af4b0366, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueLines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Not much point to keeping you locked up with no one to keep watch, is
        there?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3292689138879906966, guid: ecbba99a1b1a2e848813fba8af4b0366, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueLines.Array.data[2]'
      value: 'Luckily for you, all the cells are open, but I am here for the One
        True King...

'
